{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"15c41d5232","title":"关于统筹两广对付美蒋进犯","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"31b355f4e9","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":17,"articleId":"15c41d5232"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"1f79bc0ed3","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记、中国人民解放军广东军区司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"40d28a45b2","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"方方，当时任中共中央华南分局第三书记。"},{"id":"eed0467d54","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓，指邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记、中国人民解放军中南军区第二政治委员。谭，指谭政，当时任中共中央中南局常务委员、中国人民解放军中南军区第三政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b7ccb157c4","type":"title","text":"关于统筹两广对付美蒋进犯","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232"},{"id":"1f79bc0ed3","type":"paragraph","text":"剑英同志，并告方方可及邓、谭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232"},{"id":"40d28a45b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）你十一月廿一日动身去广西甚好。（二）广东必须迅速地和广泛地展开土地改革工作，你们布置如何盼告。（三）只要广东的土改完成，广西的土汇消灭，即使蒋介石登陆进犯也是容易对付的。（四）你们必须统筹两广，将两广作为一个对付帝国主义和蒋介石登陆进犯的统一的单位，不要只顾一省。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232"},{"id":"eed0467d54","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232"},{"id":"7f231aec3e","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232"}],"page":{"id":"212dc4bf2a","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"15c41d5232","start":371,"end":371}}}},"__N_SSG":true}